item.dc:creator: @coryallen1 coryallen1
item.description:
@coryallen1 wrote:

Does it download the cache and not connect or does it go straight to “Error Loading… Please Report”.

For Error Loading - Check to see if you have a cache auto downloader. If it is downloading from the sources owners webhost you may want to upload it to your host and change the links in the cache loader.

Another suggestion: Make sure you change the IP in gui.java aswell.
